    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/0a9c61fa1d31fdaf9e54f9802d2b3fca.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/d51e782457f533abfe12876fd642bc1c.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=100 /></span><br><br>光亮,宁静的村庄<br>有一天,村子里的一盏路灯一个盏地熄灭。<br>就这样,光从村子里消失,埋在黑暗中,女孩就向村外的塔走去。<br><br>控制着城市灯光的塔.<br>塔内有一只闪闪发光的蝴蝶。<br>为了用蝴蝶灯照亮村庄,女孩偷走蝴蝶逃跑了。<br><br>守着塔的夜女王试图杀死偷走蝴蝶的女孩,<br>经过多次曲折,女孩从塔里逃了出来。<br><br>但是因少女抢走了蝴蝶,村子里所有的光芒都消失了,<br>村子的区域消失进黑暗中。<br><br>在街上徘徊的不是人,而是影子。<br><br><br>&quot;如果再把蝴蝶放回去,说不定村子会还原。'<br><br>少女为了复回失去的光芒和村庄,再次向塔。 <br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/885b60d1e55ec30e0ea2bb9c7245e2ad.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/b72d35cf2c053d266053a7b08bbaf389.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ea1a65514e63d39c05067a6866d2a8c0.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ea1a65514e63d39c05067a6866d2a8c0.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ea1a65514e63d39c05067a6866d2a8c0.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 用光和阴影拼图<br><br>从塔上得到蝴蝶后,少女可以召唤蝴蝶。<br>召唤的蝴蝶一段时间后会消失,使用法力值能再次召唤。<br><br>用蝴蝶的光照亮灯泡,使装置启动。<br>使用各种影子,创造道路。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/287d499396a663f4a3b408496543d0d0.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/287d499396a663f4a3b408496543d0d0.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/287d499396a663f4a3b408496543d0d0.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>若在没有灯光的地方，体力会逐渐减少。<br>靠近灯光时,体力和法力值自然会恢复。<br>怪物隐藏在黑暗中，随时出现。 <br><br>有灯光时，白色的陷阱会消失,但黑色的陷阱就会出现。<br><br>相反地,在没有灯光的情况下,黑色陷阱会消失,但白色舰艇会出现。<br><br>利用陷阱以损伤怪物头目和怪兽们.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/666f0fcc56773dd129fc1221bd813703.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/666f0fcc56773dd129fc1221bd813703.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/666f0fcc56773dd129fc1221bd813703.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>受感染的村庄靠塔内的灯光维持健康<br><br>失去光芒后，村庄会复回到原本的残酷面貌。<br><br>少女为找回村庄的灯光而进入塔内。<br>每层需打败怪物头目,点燃每个部分的灯,才能恢复村庄失去的区域。 <br><br>为了拯救被黑暗吞噬的村民,需要得到塔内藏有的药草。 <br>但是塔内的各种怪物头目与夜之女王目标是杀死少女。<br><br>使用蝴蝶的光照亮塔内，解开拼图。<br>然后用塔的灯光找回失去的村庄来，也治好村民的病症。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ad7ff66818e4fe3a4224eb12a594c0cc.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ad7ff66818e4fe3a4224eb12a594c0cc.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/ad7ff66818e4fe3a4224eb12a594c0cc.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/040145344d61926e49ae54497af2edaa.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/33676886fde2349b87a4b11864fd759a.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/33676886fde2349b87a4b11864fd759a.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/33676886fde2349b87a4b11864fd759a.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/210d2cb9861feefe2845fff61206b110.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>可以用跳跃踩死或利用陷阱打败怪物。<br>组合动作次数越多,恢复的体力也会越多。<br><br>控制降落速度或滑动动作以及达到更多组合动作次数。<br><br>故事没有对话,通过角色动画表示。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/948c3fceebf15c8fc3d8ae0a5986cb93.poster.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/948c3fceebf15c8fc3d8ae0a5986cb93.webm?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/948c3fceebf15c8fc3d8ae0a5986cb93.mp4?t=1615525284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/7b9ee17b26ceeda741b7fc18703c9ffc.avif?t=1615525284\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/d378a17e8669d36ed3aa93a2900fdbd1.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/a701f66fd8b083478a2d4d76fea285a0.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/f68d9c18b546f07186d819b6eb545c24.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222090/extras/29ed09ea07a873807352bdca512443f1.avif?t=1615525284\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>键盘操作可以调整。<br>键盘外，也可以使用X-box 360,PS4双休克等。",
